properties.areaDesc: Flagler Beach to Volusia-Brevard County Line 0-20 nm
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 30 at 4:03AM EST until January 30 at 4:00PM EST by NWS Melbourne FL
properties.description:
* WHAT...North winds 15 to 20 kt with gusts up to 25 kt and seas
building to 5 to 7 feet.

* WHERE...Flagler Beach to Volusia-Brevard County Line 0-20 nm.

* WHEN...Until 4 PM EST this afternoon.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Wind and wave conditions will be hazardous for small craft.
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in these conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 4 PM EST THIS AFTERNOON
